subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Fernandez González of Chile reached the BMW Open final in Munich with a 3-6, 6-4, 6-3 victory that ended the run of Younes el-Aynaoui, the oldest semifinalist on the ATP Tour since Jimmy Connors 15 years ago.
